t and 64-bit, 2008 R2, 2012 R2, 2016, 2019.</p>', 9, 6, 1, '/storage/uploads/2023/05/17/unnamed (48).webp', 0, 19299000, '2023-05-17 14:04:26', '2023-05-17 14:04:26'),
